speech:
COVID-19 vaccine will be introduced in a phased manner
with the first phase focusing on health care workers,
frontline workers and population at higher risk. The
prioritization of groups is based on the disease incidence
and prevailing pandemic situation. However, you may
contact the local health authorities if you think you fall in
the phase 1 category and have not been included.

data.text: My name is not in the priority list though i am above 50 with comorbidity how do I get my name included?
